<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Appointment Letter</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        * {
            box-sizing: border-box;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #1f2937;
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 48px 40px;
            background: white;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        .letterhead {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: flex-start;
            padding-bottom: 28px;
            margin-bottom: 36px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
        }

        .company-name {
            font-size: 22px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #111827;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            letter-spacing: -0.02em;
        }

        .company-address {
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #4b5563;
            line-height: 1.6;
            max-width: 280px;
        }

        .doc-badge {
            text-align: right;
        }

        .doc-title {
            font-size: 30px;
            font-weight: 800;
            color: #e5e7eb;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.06em;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }

        .doc-date {
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #6b7280;
        }

        .doc-date strong {
            color: #111827;
        }

        .section-label {
            font-size: 11px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.06em;
            color: #6b7280;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
        }

        .recipient {
            margin-bottom: 32px;
        }

        .recipient-name {
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #111827;
            margin-bottom: 4px;
        }

        .recipient-addr {
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #4b5563;
        }

        .subject {
            background: #f9fafb;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 16px 20px;
            margin-bottom: 28px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #111827;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        .content {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #374151;
            line-height: 1.7;
        }

        .content p {
            margin-bottom: 16px;
        }

        .details-table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            margin: 24px 0;
        }

        .details-table th {
            background: #f9fafb;
            text-align: left;
            padding: 12px 16px;
            font-size: 13px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #6b7280;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.04em;
            width: 35%;
        }

        .details-table td {
            padding: 12px 16px;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #111827;
            font-weight: 500;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #f3f4f6;
        }

        .terms-section {
            background: #f9fafb;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 24px;
            margin: 28px 0;
        }

        .terms-title {
            font-size: 13px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #111827;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.04em;
        }

        .terms-list {
            padding-left: 20px;
        }

        .terms-list li {
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #4b5563;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .signature-section {
            margin-top: 48px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
        }

        .signature-block {
            width: 44%;
        }

        .sig-label {
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #6b7280;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.04em;
            margin-bottom: 48px;
        }

        .sig-line {
            border-top: 1px solid #d1d5db;
            padding-top: 8px;
        }

        .sig-name {
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #111827;
        }

        .sig-role {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #6b7280;
        }

        .footer {
            margin-top: 48px;
            text-align: center;
            padding-top: 24px;
            border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
            color: #9ca3af;
            font-size: 12px;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="letterhead">
        <div>
            <div class="company-name">{{companyName}}</div>
            <div class="company-address">
                {{{companyAddress}}}
                {{#if companyPhone}}<br>{{companyPhone}}{{/if}}
                {{#if companyEmail}}<br>{{companyEmail}}{{/if}}
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="doc-badge">
            <div class="doc-title">APPOINTMENT</div>
            <div class="doc-date"><strong>Date:</strong> {{appointmentDate}}</div>
            {{#if refNumber}}<div class="doc-date"><strong>Ref:</strong> {{refNumber}}</div>{{/if}}
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="recipient">
        <div class="section-label">To</div>
        <div class="recipient-name">{{employeeName}}</div>
        {{#if employeeAddress}}<div class="recipient-addr">{{{employeeAddress}}}</div>{{/if}}
    </div>

    <div class="subject">Subject: Appointment as {{position}}</div>

    <div class="content">
        <p>Dear {{employeeName}},</p>
        <p>We are pleased to inform you that you have been appointed as <strong>{{position}}</strong> in the
            <strong>{{department}}</strong> department of {{companyName}}, effective from
            <strong>{{startDate}}</strong>.</p>
        <p>Your appointment is subject to the terms and conditions mentioned below and as per the company policies:</p>

        <table class="details-table">
            <tr>
                <th>Employee Name</th>
                <td>{{employeeName}}</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <th>Position</th>
                <td>{{position}}</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <th>Department</th>
                <td>{{department}}</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <th>Date of Appointment</th>
                <td>{{appointmentDate}}</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <th>Reporting Manager</th>
                <td>{{reportingTo}}</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <th>Work Location</th>
                <td>{{workLocation}}</td>
            </tr>
            {{#if probationPeriod}}<tr>
                <th>Probation Period</th>
                <td>{{probationPeriod}}</td>
            </tr>{{/if}}
        </table>

        <div class="terms-section">
            <div class="terms-title">Terms & Conditions</div>
            <ol class="terms-list">
                <li>You will be governed by the rules, regulations, and policies of the company as amended from time to
                    time.</li>
                <li>You are required to maintain confidentiality of all company information and data.</li>
                <li>Your employment is subject to satisfactory completion of probation period{{#if probationPeriod}} of
                    {{probationPeriod}}{{/if}}.</li>
                <li>You will be required to give {{#if noticePeriod}}{{noticePeriod}}{{else}}30 days{{/if}} notice in
                    writing before leaving the organization.</li>
                <li>The company reserves the right to terminate your services with appropriate notice as per company
                    policy.</li>
                <li>You will be entitled to benefits as per company policy including health insurance and paid leave.
                </li>
            </ol>
        </div>

        <p>We welcome you to our organization and look forward to a long and mutually beneficial association.</p>
        <p>Please confirm your acceptance by signing and returning a copy of this letter.</p>
        <p>Congratulations and welcome to <strong>{{companyName}}</strong>!</p>
    </div>

    <div class="signature-section">
        <div class="signature-block">
            <div class="sig-label">For {{companyName}}</div>
            <div class="sig-line">
                <div class="sig-name">{{#if hrContactPerson}}{{hrContactPerson}}{{else}}HR Manager{{/if}}</div>
                <div class="sig-role">Human Resources</div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="signature-block">
            <div class="sig-label">Employee Acceptance</div>
            <div class="sig-line">
                <div class="sig-name">{{employeeName}}</div>
                <div class="sig-role">Date: ___________</div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
        <p>This is a system-generated document. {{companyName}}</p>
    </div>
</body>

</html>